## Description {#details}

A wrapper pass for external alias analyses.

This just squirrels away the callback used to run any analyses and register their results.

Definition at line 999 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/aliasanalysis-h">AliasAnalysis.h</a>.
